title: OPI Soft Shades Nail Lacquer, Princesses Rule!
description: A light, baby pink sheer polish with glitter. This shimmery pale pink shade is a versatile addition to any nail polish collection. Use a single coat on bare nails for a natural, feminine look or wear atop other polishes for a glittery pink finish. You can also layer Princesses Rule. by itself for increased opacity. The lovely, soft pink sparkle works well on all complexions. From the OPI Princesses Charming Collection.

title: Opi Nail Lacquer, Not So Bora Pink, 0.5 Fluid Ounce
description: A rich, creamy pink with an exotic twist. Whenever you find yourself stuck in the office or in traffic staring down at your pink nails, this not so boring pink will have you longing for a tropical trip to Bora Bora.
